{"tid":1663992,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"會做連儂牆文宣嘅入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-10-19T18:30:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T19:13:09.000Z","uid":236878,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c205a4c644854158539a1127a06a18830da11e8e","tid":1663992,"uid":236878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T18:30:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />求下你哋由今日開始做多少少保護措施:<br />\n<br />\n買返set防割衣物 頸 衫 褲 手套 手袖 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">TLDR:<a href=\"https://www.bladerunner.tv/anti-slash-clothing.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bladerunner.tv%2Fanti-slash-clothing.html&d=om99xhx1cOxPLv9Q%2FbR%2FoKcrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=0f9c28ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bladerunner.tv/anti-slash-clothing.html</a><br />\n如果你真係無論點都唔肯用千幾蚊買個保障保護自己 我都唔知講咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔該你起碼zip返塊板墊喺衫度(文具鋪有 只需幾十蚊用嚟加強以下防護措施都得)</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我喺之前po見到嘅 老豆搵仔都推薦過:【突發】防割衣特登比個八折香港人<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/dyRfpT\" target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/dyRfpT</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">Q&amp;A</span> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:好貴喎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:傻豬嚟 有助養<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:呢d資源留畀前線啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:其實依家痴連儂都有機會畀藍c/支那佬襲擊 同類事件已經唔係第一次發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有次TKO又係斬連儂手足 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">所以防割裝備絕對唔係前線先需要<br />\n大家有的防具都差唔多其實係好事嚟 又唔犯法</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好諗住未有人畀人斬死就掉以輕心</span> 呢次手足畀人斬到腸都跌撚咗出嚟 <span style=\"color: red;\">如果斬上少少後果不堪設想啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span> 仲有 如果係斬頸 割斷大動脈 或者失血過多 <span style=\"color: red;\">一樣有機會致命</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:上面寫防劈斬 但唔防插喎 無用咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:True 如果用尖刀大力插落去都係可以吉穿 都會受傷都會流血 但起碼有阻擋效果 把刀唔會咁易吉得太入<span style=\"color: red;\">唔會傷咁重 </span> <br />\n<br />\nbtw加塊板墊可以有效增強防護效果 又平(幾十蚊) 又易買(文具鋪已經有得買<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:頸同衫係保護要害 咁其他買嚟做乜柒?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:你係咪唔記得咗荃灣被斬手足果件事 手足畀黑社會斬斷腳筋 <span style=\"color: red;\">有機會行唔返</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:好啦我買齊啦可以做葉問啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:屌 咪on9啦 唔係萬能咖屌 唔好諗住咁就斬極無事可以刀槍不入 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請睇情況而定 如果你有防割手套(5級)<br />\n可以選擇嘗試阻止對方攻擊(不過唔好不自量力) <br />\n<br />\n如果對方人數眾多就be water 返屋企訓覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">緊記:連儂牆唔係用嚟守 唔好作不必要犧牲</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人 反抗</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(如果呢個係寫反抗就正)<br />\n<br />\n夜已深 各位手足早抖 TST見<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b63d5091c45fda8b59c42e3669ccaf075586a9a7","tid":1663992,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T18:30:10.000Z","msg":"【1020 尖咀見】真。遊行指南參考<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://lih.kg/aksjJwU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aksjJwU</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68ef290041f3a1c6dfdeeb4728427a96b692820a","tid":1663992,"uid":236878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T18:32:40.000Z","msg":"界板墊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔知點解出唔到正字"},{"pid":"68c0839bc6b370226be125ff32b7470dda7e307b","tid":1663992,"uid":236878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T19:10:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f09e8bd44d1f4c7bfb5951a7a55f8958688eeb93","tid":1663992,"uid":130695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T19:13:09.000Z","msg":"下星期去元朗問班學生先，買定幾套俾佢地都好"}]}